"compile and run single source file without leaving vim
autocmd filetype cpp nnoremap <leader>r :w <bar> exec '!g++ -std=c++14 -Wall -Wextra '.shellescape('%').' -o '.shellescape('%:r').' && ./'.shellescape('%:r')<CR>
